T1  - Communication Within Firms: Evidence from CEO Turnovers
AU  - Impink, Stephen Michael
AU  - Prat, Andrea
AU  - Sadun, Raffaella
Y1  - 2024/04/05
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2025/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.02719
